3    water     pastelblue


[ Surface ]
$ parameters
set: c81[   36]  $ number of x pixel
set: c82[   11]  $ number of y pixel
set: c83[    1]  $ number of z pixel
set: c84[     1.0] $ unit voxel x
set: c85[     1.0] $ unit voxel y
set: c86[    10.0] $ unit voxel z
set: c87[-c81*c84/2] $ smallest x
set: c88[-c82*c85/2] $ smallest y
set: c89[-c83*c86/2] $ smallest z
set: c90[     0.00001] $ small quota

$ Unit voxel at smallest x & y
 5000 rpp c87 c87+c84 c88 c88+c85 c89 c89+c86
$ Outer region
   99 so 500
$ Main Space
